# Logs and Monitoring â€“ Advent of Cyber 2025

## Overview
This challenge introduced the importance of logs
and monitoring in detecting security incidents.

## Security Concept
Logs provide visibility into system activity and
are essential for incident detection and investigation.

## What Was Done
- Reviewed log entries
- Identified suspicious or unusual behavior
- Understood how logs support security monitoring

## Tools Used
- Log analysis interface
- Provided challenge data

## Outcome
The challenge showed how logs help detect and
understand security events.

## Key Takeaways
- Logs are critical for security visibility
- Monitoring helps detect attacks early
- Security is both offensive and defensive
